      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-24/northern-data-group-looking-to-transition-into-ai-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Northern Data Group 正寻求从加密货币转型到人工智能领域，重点是可持续性和有效性。首席运营官 Rosanne Kincaid-Smith 在“彭博市场”节目中与 Sonali Basak 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
